    <h1>PitchPulse Unlimited Subscription Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p>Welcome to PitchPulse, the soccer referee app. These terms and conditions govern your use of the PitchPulse Unlimited subscription service. By subscribing to PitchPulse Unlimited, you agree to these terms.</p>
    
    <h2>1. Subscription Service</h2>
    <p>PitchPulse offers an Unlimited subscription that grants users the ability to create and manage unlimited matches within the app. All other app functionality remains available for free to all users.</p>
    
    <h2>2. Subscription Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>The PitchPulse Unlimited subscription costs $4.99 AUD per year or the equivalent in your local currency as determined by the App Store.</li>
        <li>Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account at the confirmation of purchase.</li>
        <li>Your subscription automatically renews unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.</li>
        <li>Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>3. Automatic Renewal</h2>
    <p>Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal by going to your Account Settings after purchase.</p>
    
    <h2>4. Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time. To cancel, go to your Apple ID account settings and turn off auto-renewal. Your subscription will remain active until the end of the current billing period.</p>
    
    <h2>5. Price Changes</h2>
    <p>If the subscription price changes, you will be notified and have the opportunity to review and accept the new price before your subscription renews.</p>
    
    <h2>6. Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>Your use of PitchPulse Unlimited is subject to our Privacy Policy, which can be found at <a href="https://saturndan.github.io/PitchPulsePages/privacy.html">https://saturndan.github.io/PitchPulsePages/privacy.html</a>.</p>
    
